# AI instruction files (kept local-only, never committed)
# Reason: AI agent instructions contain repository-specific operational rules that
# should not be exposed publicly. Contributors who modify these files locally must
# not push changes — the canonical content lives outside this repo. Files are
# maintained locally and may symlink to a shared source.
